{"type": "article", "id": 22627, "title": "简洁的滴漏式咖啡设计", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-22T10:45:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 48, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115814njQsEAmoRM3KVd6P.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一款滴漏式的咖啡装置设计，设计团队 Goat Story 采用了一个实验室风格。它的主体结构是一个很简单的木制管道，有金属的关节接口，从上至下在不同的维度进行直角转折，最后在地上形成半包围的结构作为支撑，非常简洁。滴过后的咖啡汁液直接装进了圆锥玻璃瓶里，上面有清晰的刻度标示。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115812HSvlpqZO4EifMxJL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021158130grzsq6NkKEpQOvF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115813DUWe6dOGo3glHtzT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115814u6P85FDEGCQZYOS9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}